title: Viral Pro (YouTube Pop-up HD) v2.3.7 android

Requirements: 4.0 and up

Overview: Replay Player - provides high-quality sound and offers a variety of sound effects.

Description
Replay Player - provides high-quality sound and offers a variety of sound effects.
So also supports virtually all digital music formats. Supports themes. And a lot of extra features.


Unlike version Free, Full version has no ads and additional options .
In order to enable Replay Player, buy version Full.

- Several themes.
- Sound effects .
- 5 band equalizer .
- Function stereo widening .
- The function of reverberation .
- Bass Boost function .
- Visualization .
- Continuous playback function .
- Streaming enabled buffering.
- Ability redaktirovka tags.
- System AGC ( automatic gain control) to reduce the difference in volume between tracks.
- Adjust the volume and balance .
- Sleep Timer .
- Customizable widgets.
- Function to change the text color .
- Management from the lock screen .
etc.
